metadata.name: Frosted Frida
metadata.description:
Season: Spring
Collection: Strange Fashion
Designer: Coyoacán High Street Bakery
Model: Frida Kahlo

Frida Kahlo spent the springtime becoming obsessed with ice cream cakes from the best bakery in Coyoacán. She obsessed so much that she had a seamstress collaborate with the baker on designing an outfit to perfectly match this cake. The result is a frosted look, perfect for vibrant spring days.
